TPM Bindings

install  : prefix + I
upate    : prefix + U
unistall : prefix + alt + u


Clipboards

Copying From Vim:
Copying in vim goes to -> primary (unnamed)
Pasting unnamed to
    system -> middle mouse click
    tmux -> shift + insert
    other vim -> normal paste


Copying from system:
    - selecting -> primary
        pasting to:
            system -> middle mouse click
            vim -> normal
            tmux -> shift + insert | middle mouse click
    - normal copy (ctrl + c) -> clipboard
        pasting to:
            system -> ctrl + p
            vim -> "+p
            tmux -> shift + crtl + v


Copying from tmux (terminal/insert mode in vim):
    - selecting -> primary
        pasting to:
              system -> middle mouse click
              vim -> normal
              tmux -> shift + insert | middle mouse click
    - copying (copy mode y) - clipboard
        pasting to:
              system -> ctr + v
              vim -> "+p
              tmux -> prefix + p | shift + ctr + v

Summary
vim:
    copying:
        normal copying -> primary
        "+y | (visual alt+y) -> clipboard
    pasting:
        primary -> normal pasting
        clipboard -> "+p | alt+p

tmux:
    copying:
        copy mode -> clipboard
        select -> primary
    pasting:
        primary -> middle click | shift + insert
        clipboard -> shift + ctr + v


system:
    copying:
        selection -> primary
        normal copy -> clipboard
    pasting:
        clipboard -> ctrl + v
        primary -> middle click
